'''James Sherman''' (born [[1940s#1948|1948]]) is a [[Star Wars comic books|comic book]] illustrator who drew a cover of an issue in the [[Star Wars (1977)|''Marvel Star Wars'']] series. Sherman worked on various comics for [[Marvel Comics|Marvel]] and [[Wikipedia:DC Comics|DC Comics]], most notably was his pencilling on the DC series ''[[Wikipedia:Superboy|Superboy]] and the [[Wikipedia:Legion of Super-Heroes|Legion of Super-Heroes]]'' in the 1970s.

